# {{n-g|Used when giving something to someone:}} [[here]]!
#: {{zh-x|嗱，送 畀 你 㗎！|'''Here''', it's a gift for you!|C}}
# {{n-g|Used when calling someone's attention to something:}} [[there]]!; [[here]]!; [[look]]!
#: {{zh-x|嗱，佢 咪{mai6} 就係 中意 呢{nei1} 隻 錶 囉。|'''Look''', this is the watch he likes.|C}}
# {{n-g|Used (accusingly) to remind someone of a warning:}} [[see]]!
#: {{zh-x|嗱，都 叫 咗 你 唔好 食 得 咁 急 㗎 啦。|'''See'''! I told you not to eat so hastily.|C}}
